Title : Thomas Hecht
Text : '''Thomas Hecht''' (born October 31, 1960 in [[Baltimore, Maryland]]) is an [[United States|American]] pianist, composer and professor of piano, based at the Yong Siew Toh Conservatory of Music, [[National University of Singapore]] where he was appointed founding head of piano studies in 2003.<ref>{{cite web |last=Yong Siew Toh Conservatory of Music |title=Staff Profile, Professor Thomas Hecht |url=http://www.nus.edu.sg/music/01d_aboutus_faculty.03_1.html |publisher=National University of Singapore |accessdate=April 26, 2014}}</ref>

